<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - KhumaloCraft Emporium</title>
    <style>
       
        body {
            margin: 0; 
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif; 
            
        }

        header {
            background-color: #9df9ef;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0; 
            margin-bottom: 20px; 
        }

        h1, h2 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px; 
            text-align: center; 
        }

        p {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 20px; 
        }

        .background-section,
        .featured-products,
        .newsletter {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); 
            text-align: center; 
        }

        .newsletter-form {
            margin-top: 20px; 
        }

            .newsletter-form input[type="email"] {
                width: 250px; 
                padding: 10px; 
                border-radius: 5px; 
                border: 1px solid #ccc; 
            }

            .newsletter-form input[type="submit"] {
                background-color: #007bff; 
                color: #fff;
                border: none;
                padding: 10px 20px; 
                border-radius: 5px; 
                cursor: pointer; 
            }

                .newsletter-form input[type="submit"]:hover {
                    background-color: #0056b3; 
                }

      
        .testimonial-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); 
            gap: 20px; 
            justify-items: center; 
        }

        .testimonial {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: left; 
        }

            .testimonial p {
                margin-bottom: 10px; 
            }

            .testimonial .author {
                font-style: italic; 
            }

        
        .stars {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 5px;
        }

        .star {
            color: #f2b01e; 
        }

        
        .header-image {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px;
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to KhumaloCraft Emporium</h1>
    </header>
    <img src="https://tnsi.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/US-Map.jpg" alt="KhumaloCraft Emporium" class="header-image">
    <br />
    <section class="background-section">
        <h2>About KhumaloCraft Emporium</h2>
        <p>James Khumalo, a visionary entrepreneur, founded KhumaloCraft Emporium with the goal of showcasing handcrafted products globally.<br /> Our platform connects artisans worldwide with a discerning audience.</p>
        <p>We offer a scalable, accessible, and user-friendly e-commerce platform.<br /> Our vision includes providing a positive shopping experience and ensuring global accessibility.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="featured-products">
        <h2>Customer Reviews</h2>
        <div class="testimonial-grid">
            <div class="testimonial">
                <p>"Excellent quality products! I'm very satisfied with my purchase."</p>
                <div class="stars">
                    <span class="star">&#9733;</span>
                    <span class="star">&#9733;</span>
                    <span class="star">&#9733;</span>
                    <span class="star">&#9733;</span>
                    <span class="star">&#9733;</span>
                </div>
                <p class="author">- John Doe</p>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial">
                <p>"Great customer service and fast shipping. Will definitely buy again!"</p>
                <div class="stars">
                    <span class="star">&#9733;</span>
                    <span class="star">&#9733;</span>
                    <span class="star">&#9733;</span>
                    <span class="star">&#9733;</span>
                    <span class="star">&#9733;</span>
                </div>
                <p class="author">- Jane Smith</p>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial">
                <p>"Love the unique designs! KhumaloCraft Emporium has become my go-to for gifts."</p>
                <div class="stars">
                    <span class="star">&#9733;</span>
                    <span class="star">&#9733;</span>
                    <span class="star">&#9733;</span>
                    <span class="star">&#9733;</span>
                    <span class="star">&#9733;</span>
                </div>
                <p class="author">- Emily Johnson</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="newsletter">
        <h2>Subscribe to Our Newsletter</h2>
        <form class="newsletter-form" action="#" method="post">
            <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email address" required>
            <input type="submit" value="Subscribe">
        </form><br />
        <p>Sign up to receive updates on our latest products and promotions!</p>
    </section>
    <br />
</body>
</html>
